Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of algorithms and approaches to automatically extract street map data from satellite imagery, aerial imagery, and GPS trajectory datasets, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques to assist in map editing, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the curation of map datasets, which falls under databases (cs.DB).
